s.png&amp;h=2794d7b6&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\">《方舟投資主禱文》<br />\n我們在天上的母：願人都尊契媽的名為聖。<br />\n願契媽的國降臨，願契媽的電動車馳騁在地上，<br />\n如同爆升在天上。我們盼望的升幅，<br />\n求契媽今日賜給我們，又求饒恕石仔拋售的罪，<br />\n因為我們饒恕得罪SH的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見破壞性創新，拯救我們脫離短炒。<br />\n離開方舟的叛徒，定必受到地獄之火的懲罰。<br />\n因為坐貨、賺錢、移民，<br />\n全是契媽的子民，直到永遠。阿們。</p><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/pyrcfjq.gif&amp;h=9f6bf1e8&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTrello 開左Public美股認真討論區 board，慢慢搬野上去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F513A9wIT&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=cb5393ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/513A9wIT</a><br />\n<br />\n開左個美股認真討論區（全民編輯留言區），巴打可以加野上去，周末有空會整理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=97a1eab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/b/1SNId2E3</a><br />\n<br />\n記得用<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">假名</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://temp-mail.org/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftemp-mail.org%2Fen%2F&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=6a7e0562\" target=\"_blank\">https://temp-mail.org/en/</a><br />\n<br />\n記得要加左下面條link member先可以留言<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://trello.com/invite/b/1SNId2E3/b3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%88%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftrello.com%2Finvite%2Fb%2F1SNId2E3%2Fb3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2582%25A1%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25A8%258E%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%258D%2580%25EF%25BC%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E8%25BC%25AF%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%258D%2580%25EF%25BC%2589&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=90ba8a60\" target=\"_blank\">https://trello.com/invite/b/1SNId2E3/b3210a9ad8d0743204ac005aef0d25d5/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%8E%E8%AB%96%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%88%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E7%B7%A8%E8%BC%AF%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E5%8D%80%EF%BC%89</a><br />\n<br />\nP巴貼紙登報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/EVCTV2q.jpg&amp;h=6266811b&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n開市前要唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vPKp29Luryc&amp;app=desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvPKp29Luryc%26app%3Ddesktop&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=74bf31f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vPKp29Luryc&amp;app=desktop</a><br />\n<br />\n飯錢靠晒連登仔契媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://ei.marketwatch.com/Multimedia/2019/10/15/Photos/ZG/MW-HT336_Cathie_20191015123310_ZG.jpg?uuid=799f960c-ef69-11e9-a2b6-9c8e992d421e&amp;h=f5a20718&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/qVZJyjT.j